  "date": "2022-03-15T22:46:20.000Z",
  "author": "Alice Newcome-Beill",
  "content": "      <figure>      <img alt=\"The Apple Watch Series 7\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/u4_l39DGwYmgazbTsBa7JXG8W0E=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/66976955/vpavic_211006_4796_0061.15.jpg\" />        <figcaption><em>Apple’s latest Apple Watch, the Series 7, currently starts at $349 instead of $399.</em> | Photo by Vjeran Pavic / The Verge</figcaption>    </figure>  <p id=\"ozqXgk\">Thinking about picking up a new Apple Watch? It might be tempting to <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/22722533/apple-watch-series-7-review-screen-watchos-features\">order one of the Series 7 models</a>, but new hardware always comes at a premium. And while Apple’s latest wearable offers a slightly larger display and some improvements to durability, it is largely the same Apple Watch we’re familiar with. </p><p id=\"sxsAXI\">Thankfully, each Apple Watch model offers ample functionality and has seen its fair share of discounts over the last year. So which ones should you consider if you’re in the market for Apple’s popular smartwatch while trying to shop smarter?</p><p id=\"FtR5HF\">There are currently four Apple Watch models to choose from, all of which support <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2021/6/7/22463618/apple-watchos-8-features-watch-wwdc-2021\">watchOS 8</a>. The highest-end is the Apple Watch Series 7, which starts at $399. The last-gen model, the Series 6, has received a modest discount at some retailers since its release but is still usually found starting at $399 as well, at least when it’s available. If either of those models seems too expensive, however, you can save about $120 by opting for an Apple Watch SE, which will set you back $279.</p><p id=\"44jktU\">Finally, there’s the aging <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2017/11/21/16680206/apple-watch-series-3-non-lte-smartwatch-review\">Series 3</a>, the most affordable Apple Watch to date. It has a starting retail price of $199, but it frequently goes on sale. However, if you want something more future-proof, you may want to consider Apple’s newer watches, as it’s not clear how much longer Apple will issue software updates to the Series 3 beyond watchOS 8. Regardless of which model you prefer, we’ve rounded up the best Apple Watch deals below.</p><aside id=\"Yen8lP\"><div data-anthem-component=\"readmore\" data-anthem-component-data='{\"stories\":[{\"title\":\"Here are the best AirPods deals you can get right now\",\"url\":\"https://www.theverge.com/21302051/best-apple-airpods-deals\"},{\"title\":\"Here are the best iPad deals right now\",\"url\":\"https://www.theverge.com/21280354/best-ipad-deals-apple\"}]}'></div></aside><div id=\"hdRa4b\"><div data-anthem-component=\"table:10741666\"></div></div><h2 id=\"OlUIlK\">The best <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2017/11/21/16680206/apple-watch-series-3-non-lte-smartwatch-review\">Apple Watch Series 3</a> deals</h2><p id=\"c2iEiy\">The regular price for the 38mm Series 3 is $199. It’s a decent entry-level Apple Watch if you are looking for a smartwatch with reliable battery life and solid build quality — especially if the SE, Series 6, and Series 7 seem out of your price range — but it’s also not one we would recommend picking up at this point. The design is aging, the processor is slower, and its paltry 8GB of internal storage hampers some of the more recent features introduced to the Apple Watch, like the ability to store music and podcasts for offline listening.</p><p id=\"DSKChG\">If you still want to go this route, <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/1229763/9383?subId1=TheVergeAppleWatchDeals172022&amp;sourceid=imp_000011112222333344&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-Gen-3-Series-3-38mm-Space-Gray-Aluminum-Black-Sport-Band-MTF02LL-A%2F706203065%3F&amp;veh=aff\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Walmart</a> is discounting the 38mm, GPS-enabled Series 3 by $30, bringing the price down to around $169, as are <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPsLiPRehT\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Best Buy</a> and <a href=\"https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fapple-watch-series-3-gps-38mm-silver-aluminum-case-with-sport-band-white%2F-%2FA-54101058%3F&amp;subid1=VergeAppleWatchDeals031522\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Target</a>. If you prefer the bigger, 42mm configuration with GPS, it’s also on sale in <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?subId1=Verge&amp;veh=aff&amp;sourceid=imp_000011112222333344&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-Series-3-GPS-42mm-Sport-Band-Aluminum-Case%2F742230355%3Fselected%3Dtrue\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">white and black at Walmart for $199</a> instead of $229. <a href=\"https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fapple-watch-series-3-gps-aluminum-case%2F-%2FA-52978799%3Fpreselect%3D54101062%23lnk%3Dsametab&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch152022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Target</a> and <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPsY1T3ugl\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Best Buy</a> are selling the 42mm model for $199 as well, however, it’s currently only available in the black configuration.</p><div id=\"N8sVLO\"><div data-anthem-component=\"productcard:9514914\"></div></div><div id=\"zc5j8W\"><div data-anthem-component=\"productcard:10741240\"></div></div><aside id=\"RStweJ\"><div data-anthem-component=\"readmore\" data-anthem-component-data='{\"stories\":[{\"title\":\"Apple’s latest watchOS update includes a recovery mode, of sorts\",\"url\":\"https://www.theverge.com/2022/3/15/22978387/apple-watch-8-5-update-recovery-mode-iphone-restore\"},{\"title\":\"Most Apple Watch users won’t get health benefits from AFib detection, study finds\",\"url\":\"https://www.theverge.com/2022/3/2/22958156/apple-watch-heart-rhythm-detection-benefit\"}]}'></div></aside><h2 id=\"3G29qi\">The best <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/21496928/apple-watch-se-review-smartwatch-wearos-price-specs-features\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Apple Watch SE</a> deals</h2><p id=\"GaARPa\">Starting at $279 for a 40mm version or $309 for the 44mm, the Apple Watch SE is a good midrange wearable that shares some features found on the like-minded Series 6 and Series 7, including a built-in accelerometer and hand-washing detection. However, it doesn’t have the always-on display found on Apple’s latest flagships, nor does it feature blood oxygen monitoring.</p><p id=\"2ryWZk\">We’ve previously seen the base model of the Apple Watch SE go on sale for as low as $219. At the moment, however, the 40mm, GPS-equipped configuration is only available for around $249 ($30 off) at Walmart, Amazon, Best Buy, and Target. Right now, you can pick up the discounted model with a silver case and a blue Sport Band (<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Watch-GPS-Cellular-40mm/dp/B09G93BDQP/?tag=theverge02-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Amazon</a>, <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-SE-GPS-40mm-Gold-Aluminum-Case-with-Starlight-Sport-Band-Regular%2F305879066&amp;subid1=TheVergeAppleWatchDeals2142022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Walmart</a>, <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPtzj4ggHf\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Best Buy</a>, <a href=\"https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fapple-watch-se-gps-40mm-gold-aluminum-case-with-starlight-sport-band%2F-%2FA-77640222%3Fref%3Dtgt_adv_XS000000%26AFID%3Dgoogle_pla_df%26fndsrc%3Dtgtao%26DFA%3D71700000012807845%26CPNG%3DPLA_Electronics%252BShopping_Local%257CElectronics_Ecomm_Hardlines%26adgroup%3DSC_Electronics%26LID%3D700000001170770pgs%26LNM%3DPRODUCT_GROUP%26network%3Dg%26device%3Dc%26location%3D9031583%26targetid%3Dpla-897844136621%26ds_rl%3D1246978%26ds_rl%3D1248099%26gclid%3DCjwKCAjw8sCRBhA6EiwA6_IF4bHQ0tuQ7TafHWGtxdVhGT4Ul7Gpg6LkhGyx7AHyZL6k_gHjRPHn6RoC8aoQAvD_BwE%26gclsrc%3Daw.ds&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch152022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Target</a>), a gold case and a white Sport Band (<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Watch-GPS-Cellular-40mm/dp/B09G9FS5YN/?tag=theverge02-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Amazon</a>, <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-SE-GPS-40mm-Gold-Aluminum-Case-with-Starlight-Sport-Band-Regular%2F758438118&amp;subid1=TheVergeAppleWatchDeals2142022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Walmart</a>, <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPtv0Ucd71\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Best Buy</a>, <a href=\"https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fapple-watch-se-gps-40mm-gold-aluminum-case-with-starlight-sport-band%2F-%2FA-77640222%3Fref%3Dtgt_adv_XS000000%26AFID%3Dgoogle_pla_df%26fndsrc%3Dtgtao%26DFA%3D71700000012807845%26CPNG%3DPLA_Electronics%252BShopping_Local%257CElectronics_Ecomm_Hardlines%26adgroup%3DSC_Electronics%26LID%3D700000001170770pgs%26LNM%3DPRODUCT_GROUP%26network%3Dg%26device%3Dc%26location%3D9031583%26targetid%3Dpla-897844136621%26ds_rl%3D1246978%26ds_rl%3D1248099%26gclid%3DCjwKCAjw8sCRBhA6EiwA6_IF4bHQ0tuQ7TafHWGtxdVhGT4Ul7Gpg6LkhGyx7AHyZL6k_gHjRPHn6RoC8aoQAvD_BwE%26gclsrc%3Daw.ds&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch152022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Target</a>), a gold case with a pink Sport Band (<a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPtwOrltFu\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Best Buy</a>), or a gray case with a black Sport Band (<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Watch-GPS-Cellular-40mm/dp/B09G96SSLB?tag=theverge02-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Amazon</a>, <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-SE-GPS-40mm-Gold-Aluminum-Case-with-Starlight-Sport-Band-Regular%2F645876604&amp;subid1=TheVergeAppleWatchDeals2142022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Walmart</a>, <a href=\"https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fapple-watch-se-gps-40mm-gold-aluminum-case-with-starlight-sport-band%2F-%2FA-77640222%3Fref%3Dtgt_adv_XS000000%26AFID%3Dgoogle_pla_df%26fndsrc%3Dtgtao%26DFA%3D71700000012807845%26CPNG%3DPLA_Electronics%252BShopping_Local%257CElectronics_Ecomm_Hardlines%26adgroup%3DSC_Electronics%26LID%3D700000001170770pgs%26LNM%3DPRODUCT_GROUP%26network%3Dg%26device%3Dc%26location%3D9031583%26targetid%3Dpla-897844136621%26ds_rl%3D1246978%26ds_rl%3D1248099%26gclid%3DCjwKCAjw8sCRBhA6EiwA6_IF4bHQ0tuQ7TafHWGtxdVhGT4Ul7Gpg6LkhGyx7AHyZL6k_gHjRPHn6RoC8aoQAvD_BwE%26gclsrc%3Daw.ds&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch152022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Target</a>, <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPtxSkE8kY\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Best Buy</a>).</p><p id=\"NECPac\">If you’re keen on the cellular model, Amazon is selling the 40mm, LTE version in <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Watch-GPS-Cellular-40mm/dp/B09G94T2R2/?tag=theverge02-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">space gray</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Watch-GPS-Cellular-40mm/dp/B09G93YNKL/?tag=theverge02-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">gold</a> with various Sport Bands for $299 instead of $329, while Walmart has the <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-SE-GPS-Cellular-40mm-Space-Gray-Aluminum-Case-with-Midnight-Sport-Band-Regular%2F126276053&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch152022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">silver</a> and <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-SE-GPS-Cellular-40mm-Space-Gray-Aluminum-Case-with-Midnight-Sport-Band-Regular%2F637826600&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch152022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">gray</a> model for the same price. Best Buy, additionally, is offering the same deal in several colorways — including <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPtM6EgMhM\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">gold</a>, <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPtODikJRU\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">pink</a>, <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPtQTJXvGn\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">silver</a>, and <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPt9A8DGBv\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">gray</a> — with various Sport Bands.</p><p id=\"s1vbGb\">If you have a larger wrist, all of the aforementioned retailers are discounting the 44mm, GPS-equipped models, with Walmart selling the <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-SE-GPS-40mm-Silver-Aluminum-Case-with-White-Sport-Band-Regular%2F982432819&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch12022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">gold</a>, <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-SE-GPS-40mm-Silver-Aluminum-Case-with-White-Sport-Band-Regular%2F634481974&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch152022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">black</a>, and <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/1229763/9383?subId1=TheVergeAppleWatchDeals172022&amp;sourceid=imp_000011112222333344&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-SE-GPS-40mm-Silver-Aluminum-Case-with-White-Sport-Band-Regular%2F634588522&amp;veh=aff\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">silver models</a> with different Sport Bands for $279. Amazon, meanwhile, is selling the <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Watch-GPS-Cellular-40mm/dp/B09G9DT2KW/?tag=theverge02-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">silver</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Watch-GPS-Cellular-40mm/dp/B09G9FZPN5/?tag=theverge02-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">gray</a> models for the same price, and you can buy the <a href=\"https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fapple-watch-se-gps-40mm-gold-aluminum-case-with-starlight-sport-band%2F-%2FA-77640222%3Fref%3Dtgt_adv_XS000000%26AFID%3Dgoogle_pla_df%26fndsrc%3Dtgtao%26DFA%3D71700000012807845%26CPNG%3DPLA_Electronics%252BShopping_Local%257CElectronics_Ecomm_Hardlines%26adgroup%3DSC_Electronics%26LID%3D700000001170770pgs%26LNM%3DPRODUCT_GROUP%26network%3Dg%26device%3Dc%26location%3D9031583%26targetid%3Dpla-897844136621%26ds_rl%3D1246978%26ds_rl%3D1248099%26gclid%3DCjwKCAjw8sCRBhA6EiwA6_IF4bHQ0tuQ7TafHWGtxdVhGT4Ul7Gpg6LkhGyx7AHyZL6k_gHjRPHn6RoC8aoQAvD_BwE%26gclsrc%3Daw.ds&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch152022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">white version with a silver case</a> from Target. The latter retailer is <a href=\"https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fapple-watch-se-gps-40mm-gold-aluminum-case-with-starlight-sport-band%2F-%2FA-77640222%3Fref%3Dtgt_adv_XS000000%26AFID%3Dgoogle_pla_df%26fndsrc%3Dtgtao%26DFA%3D71700000012807845%26CPNG%3DPLA_Electronics%252BShopping_Local%257CElectronics_Ecomm_Hardlines%26adgroup%3DSC_Electronics%26LID%3D700000001170770pgs%26LNM%3DPRODUCT_GROUP%26network%3Dg%26device%3Dc%26location%3D9031583%26targetid%3Dpla-897844136621%26ds_rl%3D1246978%26ds_rl%3D1248099%26gclid%3DCjwKCAjw8sCRBhA6EiwA6_IF4bHQ0tuQ7TafHWGtxdVhGT4Ul7Gpg6LkhGyx7AHyZL6k_gHjRPHn6RoC8aoQAvD_BwE%26gclsrc%3Daw.ds&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch152022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">offering the same discount on the gold model</a>, too, as is <a href=\"https://bestbuy.7tiv.net/c/482924/614286/10014?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bestbuy.com%2Fsite%2Fapple-watch-se-gps-44mm-gold-aluminum-case-with-starlight-sport-band-gold%2F5706660.p%3FskuId%3D5706660%23anchor%3DproductVariations&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch152022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Best Buy</a>, where you can pick up the <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPtGZZ0w1r\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">black model</a> or one with a <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPtHHZVVaR\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">silver case and blue Sport Band</a> for the same price.</p><p id=\"vdaR0d\">For those hoping to snag the 44mm model with LTE, Amazon is <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Watch-GPS-Cellular-40mm/dp/B09G9CS8FJ/?tag=theverge02-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">selling most variants for around $329</a> ($30 off), while Walmart has the <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-SE-GPS-Cellular-40mm-Space-Gray-Aluminum-Case-with-Midnight-Sport-Band-Regular%2F567715134&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch152022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">gray</a>, <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-SE-GPS-Cellular-40mm-Space-Gray-Aluminum-Case-with-Midnight-Sport-Band-Regular%2F470760827&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch152022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">silver</a>, and <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-SE-GPS-Cellular-40mm-Space-Gray-Aluminum-Case-with-Midnight-Sport-Band-Regular%2F703133011&amp;subid1=TheVergeBestAppleWatchDealsMarch152022\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">gold</a> models for the same price. You can also buy the larger cellular model in <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPt5upEYsa\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">gray</a>, <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPt6tZXmFK\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">gold</a>, and <a href=\"https://shop-links.co/cgPt8yKSctP\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">silver</a> with various Sport Bands from Best Buy for $329.</p><div id=\"k7Seuv\"><div data-anthem-component=\"productcard:9514947\"></div></div><div id=\"Dmq74g\"><div data-anthem-component=\"productcard:10966490\"></div></div><aside id=\"dXmk1G\"><div data-anthem-component=\"readmore\" data-anthem-component-data='{\"stories\":[{\"title\":\"How to play music on your smartwatch\",\"url\":\"https://www.theverge.com/22959795/music-smartwatch-apple-samsung-fitbit-garmin-wear-os\"},{\"title\":\"Peloton adds Apple Watch integration to all of its machines\",\"url\":\"https://www.theverge.com/2022/3/9/22969632/apple-watch-peloton-fitness-wearables\"}]}'></div></aside><h2 id=\"xtEsXh\">The best <a href=\"https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-Watch-SE-GPS-44mm-Gold-Aluminum-Case-with-Pink-Sand-Sport-Band-Regular%2F804932402%3Fselected%3Dtrue&amp;sharedid=verge\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Apple</a><a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/21496141/apple-watch-series-6-review-blood-oxygen-monitor-watchos-7\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"> Watch Series 6</a> deals</h2><p id=\"oTrUCf\">While <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2021/10/8/22716438/apple-watch-series-6-removes-lineup\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">it’s no longer officially a part of Apple’s wearable lineup</a>, you can still buy the Apple Watch Series 6 at several retailers. The Apple Watch comes in two sizes, 40mm and 44mm, which 